front.title: •Affect Mind (V)
front.gametext: Plays on table. Bad Feeling Have I is canceled. Unless Inner Strength on table, opponent may use only one combat card per turn. Let Them Make The First Move may target only Undercover spies and R2-D2.
front.lore: 'What was that?' The Jedi power known as 'affect mind' is often used to create minor distractions, allowing Jedi to elude enemies rather than engage them in battle.

counterpart: I Find Your Lack Of Faith Disturbing (V) - Defensive Shield
